- [ ] Implement responsive CSS: fixed 960px width not mobile-friendly
- [ ] Remove inline styles: scattered style attributes in HTML
- [ ] Fix semantic HTML: improve heading hierarchy and structure
- [ ] Remove brain background logo from non-MEC pages

Priority 3 (Medium - Phase 3/4):
