=== DATA STRUCTURE ===

updates.json format:
[
  {
    "date": "2025-12-01",
    "title": "MICCAI 2026 in Abu Dhabi",
    "description": "Join us at MICCAI 2026 in Abu Dhabi, UAE",
    "link": "events.html",
    "type": "announcement"
  },
  {
    "date": "2025-11-15",
    "title": "MEC 2025 Submissions Open",
    "description": "Submit your educational tutorials by August 15th",
    "link": "challenge.html",
    "type": "deadline"
  }
]

Types: announcement, event, deadline, media, highlight

highlights.json format (optional):
[
  {
    "type": "metric",
    "value": "500+",
    "label": "Tutorials Created",
    "icon": "book"
  },
  {
    "type": "feature",
    "title": "Featured Tutorial",
    "description": "Deep Learning for Medical Imaging",
    "link": "materials.html#tutorial-123",
    "image": "img/featured/tutorial-123.png"
  },
  {
    "type": "testimonial",
    "quote": "MSB helped me connect with researchers worldwide",
    "author": "PhD Student, University X",
    "role": "MEC 2024 Winner"
  }
]

=== ACCESSIBILITY REQUIREMENTS ===

WCAG 2.1 Level AA Compliance:
- All images must have meaningful alt text
- Color contrast ratios minimum 4.5:1 for normal text
- Color contrast ratios minimum 3:1 for large text
- Keyboard navigation must work for all interactive elements
- Focus indicators must be visible and clear
- Form inputs must have associated labels
- Semantic HTML structure (headings, landmarks, lists)
- Skip navigation link for screen readers
- Responsive design for zoom up to 200%
- Light/dark mode must both meet contrast requirements

Testing Tools:
- WAVE Browser Extension
- axe DevTools
- Lighthouse (Chrome DevTools)
- Keyboard-only navigation testing
- Screen reader testing (NVDA/JAWS/VoiceOver)

=== PERFORMANCE TARGETS ===

Metrics (Lighthouse):
- Performance: >90
- Accessibility: >95
- Best Practices: >90
- SEO: >90

Key Optimizations:
- Image compression and modern formats
- Lazy loading for below-fold images
- Minimize render-blocking resources
- Reduce total page size to under 2MB per page
- First Contentful Paint under 2 seconds
- Largest Contentful Paint under 2.5 seconds
- Cumulative Layout Shift under 0.1

=== BROWSER SUPPORT ===

Target Browsers:
- Chrome (last 2 versions)
- Firefox (last 2 versions)
- Safari (last 2 versions)
- Edge (last 2 versions)
- Mobile Safari (iOS 12+)
- Chrome Mobile (Android 8+)

Progressive Enhancement:
- Core content accessible without JavaScript
- CSS Grid with Flexbox fallback for older browsers
- backdrop-filter with solid background fallback
- Modern features gracefully degrade

=== DEPLOYMENT ===

Process: Simple GitHub push to master branch
- No build step required
- No compilation or bundling
- Static files served directly by GitHub Pages
- Changes go live automatically after push
- DNS: miccai-sb.github.io

Testing before push:
- Local server: python3 -m http.server 8000
- Test all pages and interactions
- Verify responsive behavior
- Check light/dark mode toggle
- Validate JSON syntax

